<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/155898-appropriate-for-a-mature-15-year-old">Appropriate for a mature 15-year-old reader?

How much sexual content/violence is there?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_155898'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11761.Underworld">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/155898-appropriate-for-a-mature-15-year-old">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/155898-appropriate-for-a-mature-15-year-old">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/32882628-jeff"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1497839387i/32882628._UY100_CR38,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/32882628-jeff">Jeff</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Absolutely appropriate. The sex is nothing major or graphic, and their is barely any violence throughout. I am not sure how many of the references a 1<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Absolutely appropriate. The sex is nothing major or graphic, and their is barely any violence throughout. I am not sure how many of the references a 15 year old will get, but I would let my niece read it and she just turned 16.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
